data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-bedroom, 1.1-bath Townhouse in Diamond Bay, with Attached 1-car garage in School District 204. The main level includes a large Family Room with adjacent Dining Room, Eat-In kitchen with breakfast bar and a lower level powder room. The Dining area is adjacent to the SGDs leading to the private patio and ample yard space. The spacious main Bedroom includes a large closet and built-in Dressing Table. The Laundry is conveniently located on the 2nd Floor in the loft area. HOA allows Rentals and Pets. Close to Shopping, major Roads and Parks and more! Unit Sold As-Is. Can close quickly!
